PersonalMission.Name: MT-15: Hunt Down the Hunter
PersonalMission.Description: You can turn the tide of the battle by taking out enemy tank destroyers.
PersonalMission.Hint: Think where you would position your tank destroyer if you drove one. This may be the spot where an enemy tank destroyer is hiding right now. TDs are often set up to cover the most common lanes of attack, so try hitting them from an unexpected direction.

Primary.Conditions: •  Cause 3,500 HP of damage to tank destroyers
